Linguistic Genius		KEY:Trait ~ Linguistic Genius		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.RaceTrait.Dhampir Race Trait	PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Dhampir ~ Jiang-shi-Born,Adopted Race ~ Dhampir	PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Trait ~ Linguistic Genius],[PREVAREQ:BypassTraitRestriction,1],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.RaceTrait]																				DESC:You gain a +1 trait bonus on Linguistics checks, and learn to speak and read one additional language from your list of racial languages. Linguistics is always a class skill for you.																																														ABILITY:Class Skill|AUTOMATIC|Linguistics	BONUS:SKILL|Linguistics|1|TYPE=Trait	SOURCEPAGE:p.20	BONUS:LANGUAGES|NUMBER|1
Numerological Gift	KEY:Trait ~ Numerological Gift	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.RaceTrait.Dhampir Race Trait	PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Dhampir ~ Jiang-shi-Born,Adopted Race ~ Dhampir	PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Trait ~ Numerological Gift],[PREVAREQ:BypassTraitRestriction,1],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.RaceTrait]																			DESC:When you select this trait, roll 3d6. The resulting number becomes your numerological totem and can never be changed. Once per day, when you roll your totem number on a d20 (such as an attack roll, save, or skill check), you may treat that roll as if you had rolled a natural 20 on the die.																																										SOURCEPAGE:p.20
Mind Trapper		KEY:Trait ~ Mind Trapper		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.RaceTrait.Dhampir Race Trait	PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Dhampir ~ Moroi-Born,Adopted Race ~ Dhampir		PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Trait ~ Mind Trapper],[PREVAREQ:BypassTraitRestriction,1],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.RaceTrait]																				DESC:You gain a +2 trait bonus on Charisma checks to convince an ally enchanted by one of your charm spells (such as charm person or charm monster) to do things it wouldn't normally do.																																																													SOURCEPAGE:p.20
Sensual Graces		KEY:Trait ~ Sensual Graces		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.RaceTrait.Dhampir Race Trait	PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Dhampir ~ Moroi-Born,Adopted Race ~ Dhampir		PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Trait ~ Sensual Graces],[PREVAREQ:BypassTraitRestriction,1],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.RaceTrait]																				DESC:Your unearthly beauty enchants those who court you. You gain a +2 trait bonus on Bluff checks made against humanoids who would be attracted to you.																																																																		SOURCEPAGE:p.20
Old Before Your Time	KEY:Trait ~ Old Before Your Time	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.RaceTrait.Dhampir Race Trait	PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Dhampir ~ Nosferatu-Born,Adopted Race ~ Dhampir	PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Trait ~ Old Before Your Time],[PREVAREQ:BypassTraitRestriction,1],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.RaceTrait]																			DESC:Any creature trying to discern your true age must make a Perception or Sense Motive check opposed by your Bluff check; you gain a +5 trait bonus on this check. You gain a +2 trait bonus on Disguise checks if your disguise makes you look at least one age category older, and ignore the check penalty for disguising yourself as a different age category while doing so.																														SOURCEPAGE:p.21
Thrall Spotter		KEY:Trait ~ Thrall Spotter		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.RaceTrait.Dhampir Race Trait	PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Dhampir ~ Nosferatu-Born,Adopted Race ~ Dhampir	PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Trait ~ Thrall Spotter],[PREVAREQ:BypassTraitRestriction,1],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.RaceTrait]																				DESC:Your heritage gives you an understanding of the powers of domination. You gain a +5 trait bonus on Sense Motive checks made to determine whether a creature is acting under the effects of a charm or compulsion.																																																								SOURCEPAGE:p.21
Half-Forgotten Secrets	KEY:Trait ~ Half-Forgotten Secrets	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.RaceTrait.Dhampir Race Trait	PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Dhampir ~ Vetala-Born,Adopted Race ~ Dhampir		PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Trait ~ Half-Forgotten Secrets],[PREVAREQ:BypassTraitRestriction,1],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.RaceTrait]																			DESC:A whisper of knowledge was transferred to you at the time of your creation. You gain a +l trait bonus on checks with two Knowledge skills of your choice, and one of these skills becomes a class skill.																												MULT:YES	CHOOSE:SKILL|TYPE=Knowledge	SELECT:2	TEMPLATE:Half-Forgotten Secrets								BONUS:SKILL|%LIST|1|TYPE=Trait		SOURCEPAGE:p.21
Unidentifiable Appeal	KEY:Trait ~ Unidentifiable Appeal	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.RaceTrait.Dhampir Race Trait	PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Dhampir ~ Vetala-Born,Adopted Race ~ Dhampir		PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Trait ~ Unidentifiable Appeal],[PREVAREQ:BypassTraitRestriction,1],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.RaceTrait]																			DESC:The unnatural symmetry of your face gives you an attractiveness that is at once captivating but hard to quantify. You gain a +1 trait bonus on Disguise checks and a +l trait bonus on Diplomacy checks made to influence those who would be attracted to you.																																									BONUS:SKILL|Disguise|1				SOURCEPAGE:p.21
Born in the Light		KEY:Trait ~ Born in the Light		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.RaceTrait.Dhampir Race Trait																PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Trait ~ Born in the Light],[PREVAREQ:BypassTraitRestriction,1],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.RaceTrait]	PREMULT:1,[PREFACT:1,TEMPLATES,IsDhampir=True],[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Adopted Race ~ Dhampir]	DESC:You gain a +2 bonus on checks and saves affected by the Endurance feat (this bonus does not stack with the bonus granted by the Endurance feat). When your light sensitivity causes you to become dazzled, you do not take the -1 penalty on sight-based Perception checks.																																														SOURCEPAGE:p.19
Final Embrace		KEY:Trait ~ Final Embrace		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.RaceTrait.Dhampir Race Trait																PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Trait ~ Final Embrace],[PREVAREQ:BypassTraitRestriction,1],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.RaceTrait]	PREMULT:1,[PREFACT:1,TEMPLATES,IsDhampir=True],[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Adopted Race ~ Dhampir]	DESC:Like your undead ancestor, you possess an intense yearning for the touch of the living, and the hunger that dwells within you grants an unnatural strength to your grip. You gain a +2 trait bonus on grapple combat maneuver checks to pin an opponent.																																																	SOURCEPAGE:p.19

